///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

    Aeolus installation guide

///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

1) Requirement

  * Apache 2.0 +
  * PHP 5.2.0 +
  * MySQL 5.0 +

2) Installation

  * Download and uncompress "aeolus.tar.gz"
  * Put "aeolus" directory into your web server's DOCUMENT_ROOT
  * Visit "http://localhost/aeolus"
  * Done